CA Chevreux's Solca Says Hermes, BMW May Weather Crisis

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-16T11:21:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/ca-chevreux-s-solca-says-hermes-bmw-may-weather-crisis-video.html
Luca Solca, global head of European
research at CA Chevreux, a unit of Credit Agricole SA, discusses
the outlook for stocks including  Hermes International (RMS)  SCA and 
 Bayerische Motoren Werke AG (BMW)  amid a deepening debt crisis.  He speaks from Paris with Maryam Nemazee on Bloomberg 
Television's "The Pulse." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:56
 